list.definition: a term used to describe a friend or person you know.
list.author: Manzy
list.example: What up homes? Que pase homes?

list.definition: A place where I can poop for however long I desire.
list.author: nadc
list.example: I had dinner at Taco Bell and then I went home and spent the rest of the night on the crapper.

list.definition: Short for "homeboy", someone who is in your neighborhood.
list.author: Davos Nathan

list.definition: A word that means something different to each person who uses it.  A person's home can be the place where they live, the place they grew up, or the place where the people they care about live.  In the case of some people, home is a variable concept, changing dependant on the placement of another person or object, or a person may even consider his or her own body the only 'true' home.
list.author: Kenning
list.example: Home is where my laptop is.

list.definition:
In relationships, "getting home" is to have sex with the other person.
(as an analogy of beisball, the different steps from kissing to actually having sex, have been compared to getting 1st,2nd 3rd base, and finally "getting home")
list.author: Alex
list.example: I "got home" with my girl last night, if you know what i mean...

list.definition: home is wherever i'm with you.
list.author: hannah horrigan
list.example:
"alabama, arkansas.
home is when i'm alone with you."

list.definition: A place that you feel comfortable in. Usually a home has family, friends, and whatever makes that person happy.  A house isn't necessarily a home if there are no friends, school, job, etc. that makes the individual happy.
list.author: King's Daughter
list.example: My home is about 4 hours away from where I reside.

list.definition: What a house becomes after the person owning it has had sex in every room.
list.author: The Dude 88
list.example: Dave bought a house and within a week he only needed to pound a girl in the attic to make it a home.

list.definition: greeting term for respected person or persons
list.author: ko

list.definition: That person against whom you can rest your head and your heart and everything feels safe; the place where you are not alone.
list.author: jihgf
list.example: I know I'm home when I can be me and still feel loved.
